{"tid":1218491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《突發 第一滴血》逃犯條例通過後 第一位受害人將會是林鄭","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T16:05:38.000Z","uid":112205,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a41e3c0c4abafe4661eb87aff6c90a7944565957","tid":1218491,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥將會是逃犯條例實施後，第一個被引渡回國的香港高官<br />\n<br />\n我等香港居民將會尋求國家檢控林鄭「煽動分裂國家政權罪」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理由如下<br />\n<br />\n1. 煽動香港一百萬人遊行示威，引致暴動<br />\n2. 其家人有居英權，未能對國家盡心辦事<br />\n3. 私下推動具爭議性條例，破壞香港安定繁榮<br />\n<br />\n建制派同意的，亦將會一同清算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVrLwzF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVrLwzF.png&h=6636976d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評：支持引渡林鄭回國受審"},{"pid":"9111473482a6464a70ea9cc5daaf15e8f9149678","tid":1218491,"uid":112205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:59:36.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前讀書 讀過商鞅變法<br />\n佢最後既下場係點<br />\n<br />\n大家可以google <br />\n<br />\n有句成語典故都係由佢以來"},{"pid":"217a1649d298b2351bd82131442b535abf2ad57f","tid":1218491,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"自己簽自己 身體力行"},{"pid":"f8c558ea779a92ecd1180588a9d68d234d454e18","tid":1218491,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"217a1649d298b2351bd82131442b535abf2ad57f","tid":1218491,"uid":11818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:00:21.000Z","msg":"自己簽自己 身體力行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea67d11bd9061f6922227e2b0475d0102e5b93aa","tid":1218491,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"推！"}]}